        "title": "Fever Overview",
        "content": "Fever is a common response to infection or illness. It can indicate the body's fight against pathogens."
      },
      {
        "title": "Common Symptoms",
        "content": "- Elevated body temperature\n- Chills\n- Sweating\n- Headache\n- Muscle aches\n- Fatigue\n- Loss of appetite"
      },
      {
        "title": "When to Seek Help",
        "content": "- Persistent high fever\n- Severe headache\n- Rash or unusual skin changes\n- Difficulty breathing\n- Confusion or irritability"
      }
    ]
  }
}
